<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_529" id="263v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_529_r1l1"><expan>Hannſ<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd Nıkeln von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_529_r1l2">talheim gebrudern </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_529_r1l3"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> ~ dıe von talheım / als Jr vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> vnd eẅch <expan>erbotte<ex>n</ex></expan> habt ʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_529_r1l4">vns ʒu <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd vns gern ʒu dıenen etc das haben wır wol . ver = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_529_r1l5"><expan>nome<ex>n</ex></expan> / Vnd <expan>dank<ex>en</ex></expan> eẅch des mit fleıſʒ / vnd <expan>laſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> eẅch <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> / daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_529_r1l6">wır ʒu dıſen <expan>ʒeıt<ex>en</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> niht 
<add><ab facs="#facs_529_line_1592203118379_1910">
<del rend="strikethrough">mer </del></ab></add> leẅt beſtellen </del> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>dıen<ex>er</ex></expan> beſtellet haben </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_529_r1l7">der wır yecʒ ein genüg meynen ʒu haben / <expan>Wurd<ex>en</ex></expan> wır <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> hernach </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_529_r1l8">mer leẅt bedurffen . ſo <expan>wölte<ex>n</ex></expan> wır wol gedacht ſein . daʒ Jr des an </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_529_line_1592203144329_1937">vns begert hett / 
<del rend="strikethrough">Vnd wo wır eẅch lıeb oder dıenſt </del> etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_529_r1l12">vnd <expan>wurd<ex>en</ex></expan> wır 
<add><ab facs="#facs_529_line_1592203147727_1942">denn </ab></add> <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ıcht ʒu rat . das ſölt eẅch wol ʒuwıſſen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_529_line_1592203153970_1947"><expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> / Denn wo wır eẅch lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_529_r1l15"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> vȷ<hi rend="sup">a</hi> gallȷ </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_529" id="263v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Hanns<ex>en</ex></expan> und Nikeln von Talheim, gebrudern </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> die von Talheim, als ir uns
                                <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> und ewch
                                <expan>erbotte<ex>n</ex></expan> habt, zu uns zu
                                <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> und uns gern zu dienen etc., das haben
                        wir wol ver<expan>nome<ex>n</ex></expan> und <expan>dank<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        ewch des mit fleisz, und <expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan> ewch
                                <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz wir zu disen
                                <expan>zeit<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan> bestellet haben, der wir yecz ein genüg
                        meynen zu haben. <expan>Wurd<ex>en</ex></expan> wir
                            <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> hernach mer lewt bedurffen, so
                                <expan>wölte<ex>n</ex></expan> wir wol gedacht sein, daz ir des an
                        uns begert hett etc. Und <expan>wurd<ex>en</ex></expan> wir <add>denn</add>
<expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> icht zu rat, das sölt ewch wol zu wissen
                                <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan>. Denn wo wir ewch lieb
                                <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst etc.
                            <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> vi<hi rend="sup">a</hi> Galli. </ab>
</div>
</div></body>
